text: Hayrullah Şahinkaya (born 1 February 1934) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Amasya
title: Hayrullah Şahinkaya
